  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magisterium: Fantasy Craft</strong> is a third-person single and co-op medieval fantasy life simulator with survival and RPG elements. In Fantasy Craft you take a part of the main character who lost his father and had to move to his uncle to the village of Lovelydale to start a new adult life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn all the crafts and become a master in alchemy, potion-making, blacksmithing, carpentry, hunting, fishing, cooking, tailoring. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will meet your old friends and get acquainted with new people in the village. You can explore magnificent places full of mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your incredible journey to the fantasy world starts here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>CUT DOWN TREES AND MINE MINERAL RESOURCES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To build a house, different workbenches and craft various items you should chop trees, mine mineral resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fff9c2d0d575e35975c213de2e974040.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fff9c2d0d575e35975c213de2e974040.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fff9c2d0d575e35975c213de2e974040.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>BUILDING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your-self a nice comfortable house, furnish it and place a lot of workbenches there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/4d7ebdea87baf7e7118a1e1b5ac12b64.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/4d7ebdea87baf7e7118a1e1b5ac12b64.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/4d7ebdea87baf7e7118a1e1b5ac12b64.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>HUNT, FISH</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive in this wonderful fantasy world, you will have to hunt and go fishing. Those animals are extremely crafty and dangerous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/a2678f851cf0c5059020ac44ed78dd76.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/a2678f851cf0c5059020ac44ed78dd76.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/a2678f851cf0c5059020ac44ed78dd76.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>MAPS AND COMPASS READING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel a real immersion into the survival game! There were no google maps in ancient times😊. So, there will be no markers on the maps you have to learn how to use compass and read maps. Buy a compass and various maps from traders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/95859fc589168637b3b08aafdef8bde2.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/95859fc589168637b3b08aafdef8bde2.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/95859fc589168637b3b08aafdef8bde2.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>COOK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fell like a real chef and go cook some delicious sophisticated food to get all sorts of buffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/70ce01fd4aa211f3420733239ec014ef.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/70ce01fd4aa211f3420733239ec014ef.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/70ce01fd4aa211f3420733239ec014ef.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>GARDEN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We heard that failure of crops led to the rise in prices for fruits and vegetables. It will be better to do gardening to get enough vegetables and fruits for cooking and winery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/6113767474c14bb3fb96eb1f0c1159e1.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/6113767474c14bb3fb96eb1f0c1159e1.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/6113767474c14bb3fb96eb1f0c1159e1.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>WINERY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can’t imagine a good dinner without a bottle of a nice wine in the end of a hard-working day. So maybe it’s time to build your own winery to craft some wine, rum, grog or beer? They say that this business pays off nicely😉.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>POTION-MAKING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to increase your health, stamina, weight, make woodcutting and mine-digging faster and more efficient, increase your critical damage and your armor - you should master the art of potion-making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/1a524aab712964b17f3ba269df78a7cc.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/1a524aab712964b17f3ba269df78a7cc.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/1a524aab712964b17f3ba269df78a7cc.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>CHALLENGING QUESTS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with diverse NPC, implementing various quests and tasks in order to get free blueprints, money and XP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>TRADE WITH NPCs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can earn money by crafting things and selling it to NPC or traders on the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/cf6b91bd78b839bbbc90fccbb42d38b1.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/cf6b91bd78b839bbbc90fccbb42d38b1.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/cf6b91bd78b839bbbc90fccbb42d38b1.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>BLACKSMITHING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As long as you stay in the village or on your land you are in no danger, but exploring new enchanted locations full of dangerous species will require excellent weapons. Take a look at blacksmith’s goods and chose the best blueprints of a weapon to fight the monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>TAILORING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t tell me you are going to explore the world without a good armor! Pay a visit to the best tailor in the village, I saw a lot of blueprints of some fine clothing to give you great protection in a combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>GO TREASURE HUNTING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want adventures, you can go treasure hunting to magnificent secret places, but you have to fight the bizarre monsters, protecting those treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fee05e6001a3b0725fb8943003c2e033.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fee05e6001a3b0725fb8943003c2e033.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fee05e6001a3b0725fb8943003c2e033.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>LOCKPICKING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the containers like chests and cupboards, that have valuable things inside like coins, lockpicks, potions, expensive tableware, food etc., are locked, make sure you buy a lot of lockpicks when going on missions into dangerous blocked areas. All locked containers have 3 difficulty levels: beginner, intermediate and master. Good luck with lockpicking 😊.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span>Features in the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBeautiful picturesque and dangerous open world locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tAlternation of day and night and weather conditions changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tThe ability to switch off the night cycle and set your hunger and thirst parameters to the minimum in the advanced settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteractive environment that gives you the opportunity to chop trees, collect sticks, stones, to mine ores and minerals, pick up plants, loot containers, lockpick chests and cabinets with valuable items and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA few variants of house building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tResearching system helps you to open new blueprints in the workbenches, you should examine plants, berries and mushrooms in the researching table to get the scrolls with recipes for future potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBrewing various potions increasing health, strength, armor, weight, crit and a lot more.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMassive quantity of blueprints in the game that involves a lot of craft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCraft various equipment, tools, weapons, amour, furniture and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteresting farming system that gives you an opportunity to cook more complex dishes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteraction with diverse wild animals and mysterious monsters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMultiple fishing zones with common and rare fish.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tLevelling up character’s skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteraction with NPCs including quests and trade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBalanced trading and economy system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA lot of quests to make loads of money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA possibility to expand your land by buying the near-by plots of land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA possibility to set complex equipment in order to mine iron, coal and copper on your land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA variety of well-protected caves with essential and rare resources.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magisterium: Fantasy Craft</strong> is a third-person single and co-op medieval fantasy life simulator with survival and RPG elements. In Fantasy Craft you take a part of the main character who lost his father and had to move to his uncle to the village of Lovelydale to start a new adult life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn all the crafts and become a master in alchemy, potion-making, blacksmithing, carpentry, hunting, fishing, cooking, tailoring. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will meet your old friends and get acquainted with new people in the village. You can explore magnificent places full of mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your incredible journey to the fantasy world starts here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>CUT DOWN TREES AND MINE MINERAL RESOURCES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To build a house, different workbenches and craft various items you should chop trees, mine mineral resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fff9c2d0d575e35975c213de2e974040.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fff9c2d0d575e35975c213de2e974040.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fff9c2d0d575e35975c213de2e974040.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>BUILDING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your-self a nice comfortable house, furnish it and place a lot of workbenches there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/4d7ebdea87baf7e7118a1e1b5ac12b64.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/4d7ebdea87baf7e7118a1e1b5ac12b64.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/4d7ebdea87baf7e7118a1e1b5ac12b64.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>HUNT, FISH</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive in this wonderful fantasy world, you will have to hunt and go fishing. Those animals are extremely crafty and dangerous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/a2678f851cf0c5059020ac44ed78dd76.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/a2678f851cf0c5059020ac44ed78dd76.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/a2678f851cf0c5059020ac44ed78dd76.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>MAPS AND COMPASS READING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel a real immersion into the survival game! There were no google maps in ancient times😊. So, there will be no markers on the maps you have to learn how to use compass and read maps. Buy a compass and various maps from traders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/95859fc589168637b3b08aafdef8bde2.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/95859fc589168637b3b08aafdef8bde2.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/95859fc589168637b3b08aafdef8bde2.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>COOK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fell like a real chef and go cook some delicious sophisticated food to get all sorts of buffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/70ce01fd4aa211f3420733239ec014ef.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/70ce01fd4aa211f3420733239ec014ef.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/70ce01fd4aa211f3420733239ec014ef.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>GARDEN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We heard that failure of crops led to the rise in prices for fruits and vegetables. It will be better to do gardening to get enough vegetables and fruits for cooking and winery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/6113767474c14bb3fb96eb1f0c1159e1.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/6113767474c14bb3fb96eb1f0c1159e1.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/6113767474c14bb3fb96eb1f0c1159e1.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>WINERY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can’t imagine a good dinner without a bottle of a nice wine in the end of a hard-working day. So maybe it’s time to build your own winery to craft some wine, rum, grog or beer? They say that this business pays off nicely😉.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>POTION-MAKING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to increase your health, stamina, weight, make woodcutting and mine-digging faster and more efficient, increase your critical damage and your armor - you should master the art of potion-making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/1a524aab712964b17f3ba269df78a7cc.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/1a524aab712964b17f3ba269df78a7cc.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/1a524aab712964b17f3ba269df78a7cc.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>CHALLENGING QUESTS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with diverse NPC, implementing various quests and tasks in order to get free blueprints, money and XP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>TRADE WITH NPCs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can earn money by crafting things and selling it to NPC or traders on the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/cf6b91bd78b839bbbc90fccbb42d38b1.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/cf6b91bd78b839bbbc90fccbb42d38b1.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/cf6b91bd78b839bbbc90fccbb42d38b1.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>BLACKSMITHING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As long as you stay in the village or on your land you are in no danger, but exploring new enchanted locations full of dangerous species will require excellent weapons. Take a look at blacksmith’s goods and chose the best blueprints of a weapon to fight the monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>TAILORING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t tell me you are going to explore the world without a good armor! Pay a visit to the best tailor in the village, I saw a lot of blueprints of some fine clothing to give you great protection in a combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>GO TREASURE HUNTING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want adventures, you can go treasure hunting to magnificent secret places, but you have to fight the bizarre monsters, protecting those treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fee05e6001a3b0725fb8943003c2e033.poster.avif?t=1767688478\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fee05e6001a3b0725fb8943003c2e033.webm?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/fee05e6001a3b0725fb8943003c2e033.mp4?t=1767688478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span><strong>LOCKPICKING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the containers like chests and cupboards, that have valuable things inside like coins, lockpicks, potions, expensive tableware, food etc., are locked, make sure you buy a lot of lockpicks when going on missions into dangerous blocked areas. All locked containers have 3 difficulty levels: beginner, intermediate and master. Good luck with lockpicking 😊.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358040/extras/baf8bed034fced9bece5e7e5050bbc2e.webp?t=1767688478\" width=500 height=10 /></span>Features in the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBeautiful picturesque and dangerous open world locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tAlternation of day and night and weather conditions changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tThe ability to switch off the night cycle and set your hunger and thirst parameters to the minimum in the advanced settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteractive environment that gives you the opportunity to chop trees, collect sticks, stones, to mine ores and minerals, pick up plants, loot containers, lockpick chests and cabinets with valuable items and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA few variants of house building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tResearching system helps you to open new blueprints in the workbenches, you should examine plants, berries and mushrooms in the researching table to get the scrolls with recipes for future potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBrewing various potions increasing health, strength, armor, weight, crit and a lot more.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMassive quantity of blueprints in the game that involves a lot of craft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCraft various equipment, tools, weapons, amour, furniture and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteresting farming system that gives you an opportunity to cook more complex dishes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteraction with diverse wild animals and mysterious monsters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMultiple fishing zones with common and rare fish.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tLevelling up character’s skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteraction with NPCs including quests and trade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBalanced trading and economy system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA lot of quests to make loads of money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA possibility to expand your land by buying the near-by plots of land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA possibility to set complex equipment in order to mine iron, coal and copper on your land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tA variety of well-protected caves with essential and rare resources.</p>",
